在幾何學中，'''星形菱形三十面體'''是指[[菱形三十面體|菱形三十面體]]的星形化體，即把菱形三十面體的面和邊沿伸直到向外相交成星形的立體。溫尼爾在他的書《[[溫尼爾多面體模型列表|多面體模型]]》中列出許多星形多面體模型，其中也收錄了一些星形菱形三十面體<ref>{{cite book | author = {{link-en|馬格努斯·J·溫尼爾|Magnus J. Wenninger|Wenninger, Magnus}} | title = Polyhedron Models | publisher = Cambridge University Press | year = 1974 | isbn = 0-521-09859-9 }}</ref>，例如[[内侧菱形三十面体|内侧菱形三十面体]]<ref name="mathworld MedialRhombicTriacontahedron">{{mathworld | urlname = MedialRhombicTriacontahedron| title = Medial Rhombic Triacontahedron}} （[http://mathworld.wolfram.com/MedialRhombicTriacontahedron.html 原始]內容[https://web.archive.org/web/20160801064119/http://mathworld.wolfram.com/MedialRhombicTriacontahedron.html 存檔]於2016-09-01）.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.software3d.com/MedialRTC.php | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304101204/http://www.software3d.com/MedialRTC.php | archivedate =2016-03-04|title = Medial Rhombic Triacontahedron | publisher = software3d.com}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
星形菱形三十面體是一種多面體類型，屬於此類的多面體數量非常龐大。埃德（Ede）在1958年時列舉了13種基本的星形菱形三十面體類型<ref>{{cite journal
  |title="Rhombic Triacontahedra"
  |author=Ede, J. D.
  |journal=Math. Gaz.
  |volume=42
  |pages=pp.98-100
  |year=1958}}</ref>。鮑萊（Pawley）在1973年時提出了一些規則以令星形菱形三十面體可以完全被枚舉<ref name="Pawley1975">{{cite journal
  |title="The 227 triacontahedra."
  |author=Pawley, G. S.
  |journal=Geometriae Dedicata
  |volume=4
  |issue=2
  |doi=10.1007/BF00148756
  |pages=pp.221-232
  |date=1975-08-01}}</ref>。

這些多面體種類繁多，大多都並未被觀察及描繪，因此大多數並未命名。梅塞爾（Messer）在1995年描述了其中227個星形化體<ref>{{cite journal
  |title="Stellations of the Rhombic Triacontahedron and Beyond."
  |author=Messer, P. W.
  |journal=Structural Topology
  |volume=21
  |pages=pp.25-46
  |year=1995}}</ref>（含原像菱形三十面體在內，即1種凸多面體和226種星形多面體<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.georgehart.com/virtual-polyhedra/srtc-index.html | title = List of Stellations of the Rhombic Triacontahedron | author = George W. Hart | publisher = Virtual Polyhedra | year = 1996 | accessdate = 2020-08-17 | archive-date = 2019-12-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191230064839/http://georgehart.com/virtual-polyhedra/srtc-index.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www3.mpifr-bonn.mpg.de/staff/pfreire/polyhedra/rhombic_triacontahedron.html | title = Stellations of the Rhombic Triacontahedron | author = Paulo Freire | publisher = mpifr-bonn.mpg.de | year = 1996 | accessdate = 2020-08-17 | archive-date = 2019-05-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190504132735/https://www3.mpifr-bonn.mpg.de/staff/pfreire/polyhedra/rhombic_triacontahedron.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>）。

== 種類 ==
菱形三十面體透過全部匹配能產生227種星形菱形三十面體<ref name="Webb, R. Enumeration">{{Cite web | url = https://www.software3d.com/Enumerate.php | author = Webb, R. | title = "Enumeration of Stellations." | publisher = software3d.com | access-date = 2019-09-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190427002618/https://www.software3d.com/Enumerate.php | archive-date = 2019-04-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，其中包括了115個鏡像不變的立體和112個具有手性鏡像的立體；透過[[五十九種二十面體#米勒的規則|米勒的規則]]<ref name="a brief history">{{cite web | url = http://www.steelpillow.com/polyhedra/StelFacet/history.html | title = ''Stellation and facetting - a brief history'' | author = Guy's | website = steelpillow.com | date = 2010-12-19 | accessdate = 2016-03-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304214440/http://www.steelpillow.com/polyhedra/StelFacet/history.html | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>
可以產生358833098種星形菱形三十面體，其中包括了84959個鏡像不變的立體和358748139種具有手性鏡像的立體<ref name="Webb, R. Enumeration"/>。

=== 已命名的星形菱形三十面體 ===
{{Anchor|列表}}已命名的星形菱形三十面體十分少，其命名的原因多半與星形菱形三十面體無關，而是因為其他研究的同時剛好研究的立體屬於星形菱形三十面體，例如五複合立方體雖是一種星形菱形三十面體<ref name="georgehart srtc-info">{{cite web | url = http://www.georgehart.com/virtual-polyhedra/srtc-info.html | title = Stellations of the Rhombic Triacontahedron | author = George W. Hart | publisher = Virtual Polyhedra | year = 1996 | accessdate = 2020-08-17 | archive-date = 2019-12-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191229225950/http://georgehart.com/virtual-polyhedra/srtc-info.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但其因為是立方體複合體的相關研究而得名<ref name="mathworld Cube5-Compound">{{mathworld|urlname=Cube5-Compound |title= Compound of Five Cubes}}</ref>。

==== 黃金一百二十面體 ====
[[File:First_stellation_of_rhombic_triacontahedron.svg|thumb]]
第一星形菱形三十面體，又稱黃金一百二十面體，是菱形三十面體星形化的第一種形式，其對應形狀轉化為間單多面體（即去除自相交面隱沒於立體內部的面）後聳形成的立體共由120個面、62個頂點和180條邊組成，且五種柏拉圖立體皆可以共用頂點地嵌入這個立體中。<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://web.ac-noumea.nc/static/maths/polyhedr/Dennis_.htm | title = Lynnclaire Dennis' polyhedra | publisher=ac-noumea.nc|date=2005-06-25}}</ref>

