== 用途 ==
部分星形菱形三十面體被一些數學學者認為是具代表性的立體，用於一些與幾何學相關著作的封面或標誌，例如[[大菱形三十面體|大菱形三十面體]]<ref name="Coxeter 1973">Coxeter, H. S. M. Regular Polytopes, 3rd ed. New York: Dover, p. 103, 1973. ISBN 978-0486614809</ref><ref name="mathworld GreatIcosidodecahedron"/>和[[菱形六十面體|菱形六十面體]]<ref group="lower-roman">{{Cite web | url=https://blog.wolframalpha.com/2009/05/19/whats-in-the-logo-that-which-we-call-a-rhombic-hexecontahedron | author=Weisstein, E. W | title="What's In a Name? That Which We Call a Rhombic Hexecontahedron." | date=2009-05-19 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2020-02-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200215120750/http://blog.wolframalpha.com/2009/05/19/whats-in-the-logo-that-which-we-call-a-rhombic-hexecontahedron/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="the-story-of-spikey">{{Cite web | url=https://writings.stephenwolfram.com/2018/12/the-story-of-spikey/ | author=Weisstein, E. W | title="the-story-of-spikey" | date=2018-12-28 | accessdate=2020-08-20 | archive-date=2020-07-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718142655/https://writings.stephenwolfram.com/2018/12/the-story-of-spikey/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。前者被用於多面體領域著名著作《正多胞形》的封面上<ref name="Coxeter 1973"/><ref name="mathworld GreatIcosidodecahedron"/>，後者為[[Wolfram_Alpha|Wolfram Alpha]]的[[标志|标志]]。<ref name="the-story-of-spikey"/>

